org.openwms.common.units

Class UnitUserType

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openwms.common.units.UnitUserType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.hibernate.usertype.CompositeUserType

    public class UnitUserType
extends Object
implements org.hibernate.usertype.CompositeUserType
    An UnitUserType is used by Hibernate as converter for custom Unit types. Only subclasses of AbstractMeasure are supported by this type converter.
    Author:
    Heiko Scherrer
